net.bytebuddy.dynamic.scaffold.subclass

Class SubclassInstrumentationContextDelegate

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.bytebuddy.dynamic.scaffold.subclass.SubclassInstrumentationContextDelegate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TypeWriter.MethodPool, Instrumentation.Context.Default.AuxiliaryTypeNamingStrategy, AuxiliaryType.MethodAccessorFactory

    public class SubclassInstrumentationContextDelegate
extends Object
implements AuxiliaryType.MethodAccessorFactory, Instrumentation.Context.Default.AuxiliaryTypeNamingStrategy, TypeWriter.MethodPool
    A delegate class that represents a method accessor factory for an instrumentation where an instrumentation is conducted by creating a subclass of a given type. This delegate represents a mutable data structure.

      • getProxiedMethods

        public Iterable<MethodDescription> getProxiedMethods()
        Returns an iterable containing all accessor methods that were registered with this delegate. The iterable can safely be co-modified in the same thread in order to allow the registration of additional accessor methods with this delegate while other accessors are already created for the instrumented type.
        Returns:
        An co-modifiable iterable of all accessors method that were registered with this delegate.
